snippet.description:
The 2020 Pipeline masters was pretty special. After the first day of competition, the contest was put on hold due to some Covid 19 cases within the event. Finally the World Surf League was able to resume competition, waves were absolutely firing and Leonardo Fioravanti made the Quarter finals to start his 2021 Championship tour campaign

